OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBlustery
OL,6,Fshowers continuing this evening and to
OL,7,Fstart the night. Drier with clear
OL,8,Fspells and the wind easing during the
OL,9,Fsecond half of the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FDry with cloudy periods to
OL,12,Fstart the day, showers developing in
OL,13,Fthe afternoon and evening but not as
OL,14,Ffrequent or as heavy compared to
OL,15,FThursday. Wind continuing to ease.
